{"tid":2200280,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–利用家庭電器散發熱力的發電可能性","createTime":"2020-09-12T21:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T12:08:12.000Z","uid":38861,"like":45,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"53f675076fe28af7f5b344e5c7aaeac4b26e2197","tid":2200280,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T21:35:42.000Z","msg":"雪櫃、冷氣機、水煲等等各電器不時都會散發出熱力。<br />\n如果將這些多餘的熱力轉化成為電力，便能夠更有效運用資源，不作浪費。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NA87Ykn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNA87Ykn.jpg&h=f2a54090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）繼續深入講解之前，我們先以非常簡單的方法概括一下發電的原理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HrA7dO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HrA7dO.jpg&h=39ef9c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要電子在閉合電路單方向流動，就能促成電流，提供電力讓燈泡發光。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）要把熱力有效轉化為電力，我們需要一樣能夠有效傳遞電子而同時又不會傳遞熱力的物料。<br />\n<br />\n有科學家最近發表文章（Ref1)，利用化學物ferricyanide ion Fe(CN)6 &ndash;4作為媒體把熱力轉化為電力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2X5usdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2X5usdT.jpg&h=82ed7c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n選用Fe(CN)6 &ndash;4的原因基於其兩種特質。<br />\n<br />\n1.它遇冷（約攝氏20度左右）的時候，再加上Guanidinium ion的輔助下便會變成固體結晶。<br />\n<br />\n2.它遇熱的時候會放出電子並成為Fe(CN)6 &ndash;3。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）以下就是利用熱力發電的精髓要點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ix5NYkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fix5NYkC.jpg&h=a3536f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.Fe(CN)6 &ndash;4遇上外間熱力（例如電器所散發出的熱力），因而會釋發電子並成為Fe(CN)6 &ndash;3。<br />\n<br />\n2.電子在閉合電路走動，產生電流，讓燈泡發亮。<br />\n<br />\n3.電子到達另一端的凍金屬棒（約攝氏20度）後，從第1點所得來的Fe(CN)6 &ndash;3便會接收電子，變回Fe(CN)6 &ndash;4。<br />\n<br />\n4.Fe(CN)6 &ndash;4在Guanidinium ion的輔助下變成固體結晶。<br />\n固體相對上傳熱的能力比液體較弱，因而減低了熱金屬棒把熱力傳到凍金屬棒的效率，促使凍金屬棒及熱金屬棒維持著溫差。<br />\n<br />\n5.在地心吸力的影響下，固體結晶會趨往金屬棒那方。而在熱力的影響下，固體結晶變回液態Fe(CN)6 &ndash;4，重回第1點不斷循環。<br />\n<br />\n綜合來說，科學家巧妙利用了Fe(CN)6 &ndash;4遇熱釋出電子的特點，以及遇冷配合Guanidinium結成固體、固體不易傳熱的特質，建造了有效傳遞電子而同時又不會有效傳遞熱力的物料。<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）科學家在文中亦嘗試利用20個圖4的模組，在兩極維持50度的溫差下，提供電力予各用途之上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1iG2Nw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1iG2Nw.jpg&h=27bd8c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在需要解決的問題，就是找出收集多餘熱力的有效方法及物料，引導熱力到模組裡頭。<br />\n文章作者表示現時已積極尋找物料，相信假以時日絕有可能會在市面見到收集電器熱力發電的設備。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513TsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=a879e75f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513TsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=ec7da626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2020/09/09/science.abd6749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2020%2F09%2F09%2Fscience.abd6749&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513TsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=74e8d3f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2020/09/09/science.abd6749</a>"},{"pid":"52a3e4f62df5db7a84b955da85755c6061a01286","tid":2200280,"uid":58642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T22:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0494f69bf592d2c02ce0c20c8af2a081dd8a19a9","tid":2200280,"uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T23:18:26.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acf5ca95a23308995b2b3d52ed0630e29775806","tid":2200280,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T23:20:29.000Z","msg":"再極端啲 室溫發電可唔可行"},{"pid":"ec540ef583f162fce8cc99f0ac422f4cfa34c26c","tid":2200280,"uid":89064,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3acf5ca95a23308995b2b3d52ed0630e29775806","tid":2200280,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T23:20:29.000Z","msg":"再極端啲 室溫發電可唔可行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T23:30:36.000Z","msg":"可行既話。。都唔好咁張揚。。tesla..."},{"pid":"f8823fbd3e928ae39040bc19b385725a29893f89","tid":2200280,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T23:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f4f25babc0663b6a8010b115385672756b251e","tid":2200280,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T23:58:04.000Z","msg":"熱回收不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b7aec3991c0eb5055ef52e2287036b4f8e09fd","tid":2200280,"uid":176553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"水煲煲水唔係廢熱當然可行，雪櫃冷氣唔使諗，廢熱散唔切架雪櫃冷氣隨時overheat。不如你諗下點樣可以唔整壞粒CPU嘅情況下又可以散熱又轉化做電能？"},{"pid":"ba02544dc50d8654ab9e6b08f1dae08cdc1d1ef6","tid":2200280,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4b7aec3991c0eb5055ef52e2287036b4f8e09fd","tid":2200280,"uid":176553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"水煲煲水唔係廢熱當然可行，雪櫃冷氣唔使諗，廢熱散唔切架雪櫃冷氣隨時overheat。不如你諗下點樣可以唔整壞粒CPU嘅情況下又可以散熱又轉化做電能？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:30:00.000Z","msg":"其實將熱能變電力，現時已經有，不過要靠稀土系列金屬整。"},{"pid":"201da2193d2abc0da5896af60445c4792a39fad5","tid":2200280,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T02:01:55.000Z","msg":"但個module自己又有heat lost，可以整另一個module吸熱發電，如此類推"},{"pid":"3fb38f97443c8b4e398596a3ab02ad02d161d6ff","tid":2200280,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:22:56.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1880363fa49bdc88ad1692e3eff40398240bd868","tid":2200280,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"永動機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c085040e9553a5890ab2ea04a376188b9123ac","tid":2200280,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"咁不如直接攞出去太陽曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c389a55d80908ba6602ebd2f0cdfda1b8ba4196","tid":2200280,"uid":202256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3acf5ca95a23308995b2b3d52ed0630e29775806","tid":2200280,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T23:20:29.000Z","msg":"再極端啲 室溫發電可唔可行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"室溫應該唔可行<br />\n用熱力發電嘅要有溫差先得"},{"pid":"49033973e0c010e512114cf2e3f0f5f062f71794","tid":2200280,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3acf5ca95a23308995b2b3d52ed0630e29775806","tid":2200280,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T23:20:29.000Z","msg":"再極端啲 室溫發電可唔可行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:49:27.000Z","msg":"唔得<br />\n<br />\n一定要有足夠溫差，<br />\n<br />\n熱能係一定由熱去凍， 兩件唔同溫度既嘢最終係會一樣溫度<br />\n<br />\n即係你唔能夠儲起電器所產生既無用既熱能"},{"pid":"4ca14e0bbdd928985cb040b34175818d160a178d","tid":2200280,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"想問Guanidinium ion 要點樣先畀到FeCN嚟融化？ 一直供應？定係喺條rod入面？<br />\n利申 冇chem底"},{"pid":"eb0a6dad21b08bb14ba185455c1276fb5d9d3ae1","tid":2200280,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ca14e0bbdd928985cb040b34175818d160a178d","tid":2200280,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"想問Guanidinium ion 要點樣先畀到FeCN嚟融化？ 一直供應？定係喺條rod入面？<br />\n利申 冇chem底"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"篇文話係凍金屬棒個邊加入去，詳情我都唔係好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n不過就算Guanidinium ion一直係入面都無所謂，始終作係凍嗰邊（~20C）先會幫到手形式結晶，遇熱就會融化變為液體。"},{"pid":"49c0a6f5a23cfd41ee8b5e165aa3a355b193c373","tid":2200280,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb0a6dad21b08bb14ba185455c1276fb5d9d3ae1","tid":2200280,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ca14e0bbdd928985cb040b34175818d160a178d","tid":2200280,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"想問Guanidinium ion 要點樣先畀到FeCN嚟融化？ 一直供應？定係喺條rod入面？<br />\n利申 冇chem底"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"篇文話係凍金屬棒個邊加入去，詳情我都唔係好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n不過就算Guanidinium ion一直係入面都無所謂，始終作係凍嗰邊（~20C）先會幫到手形式結晶，遇熱就會融化變為液體。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3b14f731541ca3aedc0907f1e8a81a5ff65e66","tid":2200280,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:34:53.000Z","msg":"收集閃電會唔會好d"},{"pid":"482d54b80b29e620aa8a39f84a05e9dc54ceeefb","tid":2200280,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c3b14f731541ca3aedc0907f1e8a81a5ff65e66","tid":2200280,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:34:53.000Z","msg":"收集閃電會唔會好d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"計產電效率的話，當然有好多方法更勝一籌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家文章作者的原意係想將一啲日常產生出的多餘熱力轉化為電力，物盡其用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f58ca60819f144354fa9aa278ef090c65f929d","tid":2200280,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c3b14f731541ca3aedc0907f1e8a81a5ff65e66","tid":2200280,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:34:53.000Z","msg":"收集閃電會唔會好d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"會唔會難predict左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263789c6c9d7fc107c216034bc3eb21c147466bb","tid":2200280,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}